 Lady]]'' (1937)\n| ''[[Michel Strogoff (1936 film)|Michel Strogoff]]'' (1936)\n| The novel ''[[Michael Strogoff]]'' ([[Jules Verne]])\n|-\n| ''[[Some Like It Hot]]'' (1959)\n| ''[[Fanfare d'amour]]'' (1935)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Sommersby]]'' (1993)\n| ''[[Le Retour De Martin Guerre]]'' (1982)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Sorcerer (film)|Sorcerer]]'' (1977)\n| ''[[The Wages of Fear|Le Salaire de la Peur]]'' (1953)\n| The novel ''Le Salaire de la peur'' ([[Georges Arnaud]])\n|-\n| ''[[Special Correspondents]]'' (2016)\n| ''[[Envoy\u00e9s tr\u00e8s sp\u00e9ciaux]]'' (2009)\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Station Six-Sahara]]'' (1962)\n| ''[[S.O.S. Sahara]]'' (1938, Germany)\n| The play ''Men Without a Past'' (Jean Martet)\n|-\n| ''[[Stranger in the House (1967 film)|Stranger in the House]]'' (1967)\n| ''[[The Strangers in the House (film)|Les Inconnus dans la maison]]'' (1942)\n| The novel ''[[The Strangers in the House]]'' ([[Georges Simenon]])\n|-\n| ''[[Sweet Devil]]'' (1938)\n| ''[[Quelle dr\u00f4le de gosse!]]'' (1935)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[The Talented Mr. Ripley (film)|The Talented Mr. Ripley]]'' (1999)\n| ''[[Purple Noon|Plein soleil]]'' (1960)\n| The novel ''[[The Talented Mr. Ripley]]'' ([[Patricia Highsmith]])\n|-\n| ''[[Taxi (2004 film)|Taxi]]'' (2004)\n| ''[[Taxi (1998 film)|Taxi]]'' (1998)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Temptation Harbour]]'' (1947)\n| ''L'Homme de Londres'' (1943)\n| The novel ''Newhaven-Dieppe (L'Homme de Londres)'' ([[Georges Simenon]])\n|-\n| ''[[Three Fugitives]]'' (1989)\n| ''[[Les Fugitifs]]'' (1986)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Three Maxims]]'' (1936)\n| ''{{ill|Vari\u00e9t\u00e9s (film)|fr|3=Vari\u00e9t\u00e9s (film, 1935)|lt=Vari\u00e9t\u00e9s}}'' (1935)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Three Men and a Baby]]'' (1987)\n| ''[[Three Men and a Cradle|Trois hommes et un couffin]]'' (1985)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[The Tourist (2010 film)|The Tourist]]'' (2010)\n| ''[[Anthony Zimmer]]'' (2005)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Tovarich (film)|Tovarich]]'' (1937)\n| ''[[Tovaritch (film)|Tovaritch]]'' (1935)\n| The play ''Tovaritch'' ([[Jacques Deval]])\n