stria)\n| The operetta ''[[Ball im Savoy]]'' ([[Paul Abraham]], [[Alfred Gr\u00fcnwald (librettist)|Alfred Gr\u00fcnwald]], [[Fritz L\u00f6hner-Beda]])\n|-\n| ''[[Beauty and the Boss]]'' (1932)\n| ''[[Poor as a Church Mouse]]'' (1931)\n| The play ''A templom eg\u00e9re'' ([[Ladislas Fodor]])\n|-\n| ''[[Between Us Girls]]'' (1942)\n| ''[[A Precocious Girl]]'' (1934, Austria)\n| The play ''Le Fruit Vert'' (Jacques Th\u00e9ry, Regis Gignoux)\n|-\n| ''[[The Blue Angel (1959 film)|The Blue Angel]]'' (1959)\n| ''[[The Blue Angel]]'' (1930)\n| The novel ''[[Professor Unrat]]'' ([[Heinrich Mann]])\n|-\n| ''[[Bundle of Joy]]'' (1956)\n| ''[[Little Mother (1935 film)|Little Mother]]'' (1935, Austria)\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Burning Secret]]'' (1988)\n| ''[[The Burning Secret]]'' (1933)\n| The short story ''Brennendes Geheimnis'' ([[Stefan Zweig]])\n|-\n| ''[[The Captain from K\u00f6penick (1945 film)|The Captain from K\u00f6penick]]'' (1945)\n| ''[[The Captain from K\u00f6penick (1931 film)|The Captain from K\u00f6penick]]'' (1931)\n| The play ''Der Hauptmann von K\u00f6penick'' ([[Carl Zuckmayer]]), based on [[Wilhelm Voigt]]\n|-\n| ''[[The Challenge (1938 film)|The Challenge]]'' (1938)\n| ''[[Struggle for the Matterhorn]]'' (1928, Switzerland)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[The Church Mouse]]'' (1934)\n| ''[[Poor as a Church Mouse]]'' (1931)\n| The play ''A templom eg\u00e9re'' ([[Ladislas Fodor]])\n|-\n| ''[[City of Angels (film)|City of Angels]]'' (1998)\n| ''[[Wings of Desire|Der Himmel \u00fcber Berlin]]'' (1987, West Germany)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Confession (1937 film)|Confession]]'' (1937)\n| ''[[Mazurka (film)|Mazurka]]'' (1935)\n|\n|-\n| ''[[The Countess of Monte Cristo (1934 film)|The Countess of Monte Cristo]]'' (1934)\n| ''[[The Countess of Monte Cristo (1932 film)|The Countess of Monte Cristo]]'' (1932)\n|\n|-\n| ''[[The Countess of Monte Cristo (1948 film)|The Countess of Monte Cristo]]'' (1948)\n| ''[[The Countess of Monte Cristo (1932 film)|The Countess of Monte Cristo]]'' (1932)\n|\n|-\n| 