]]'' (1954)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Godzilla (2014 film)|Godzilla]]'' (2014)\n| ''[[Godzilla (1954 film)|Gojira]]'' (1954)\n|\n|-\n| ''[[The Grudge]]'' (2004)\n| ''[[Ju-On: The Grudge]]'' (2002)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[The Grudge (2020 film)|The Grudge]]'' (2020)\n| ''[[Ju-On: The Grudge]]'' (2002)\n|\n|-\n| ''[[The Guardian (2006 film)|The Guardian]]'' (2006)\n| ''[[Umizaru (film)|Umizaru]]'' (2004)\n|  \n|-\n| ''[[Hachi: A Dog's Tale]]'' (2010)\n| ''[[Hachiko Monogatari]]'' (1987)\n|\n|-\n| ''Iron Maze'' (1991)<!--Director: Hiroaki Yoshida; Starring: Jeff Fahey, Bridget Fonda, Hiroaki Murakami-->\n| ''[[Rashomon]]'' (1950)\n| The short stories \"[[Rash\u014dmon (short story)|Rash\u014dmon]]\" and \"[[In a Grove]]\" ([[Ry\u016bnosuke Akutagawa]])\n|-\n| ''[[Last Man Standing (1996 film)|Last Man Standing]]'' (1996)\n| ''[[Yojimbo]]'' (1961)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[The Magnificent Seven]]'' (1960)\n| ''[[Seven Samurai]]'' (1954)\n|\n|-\n| ''[[The Magnificent Seven (2016 film)|The Magnificent Seven]]'' (2016)\n| ''[[Seven Samurai]]'' (1954)\n|-\n| ''[[Midnight Sun (2018 film)|Midnight Sun]]'' (2018)\n| ''[[A Song to the Sun|Midnight Sun]]'' (2006)\n|\n|-\n| ''[[One Missed Call (2008 film)|One Missed Call]]'' (2008)\n| ''[[One Missed Call (2003 film)|Chakushin Ari]]'' (2003)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[The Outrage]]'' (1964)\n| ''[[Rashomon]]'' (1950)\n| The short stories \"[[Rash\u014dmon (short story)|Rash\u014dmon]]\" and \"[[In a Grove]]\" ([[Ry\u016bnosuke Akutagawa]])\n|-\n| ''[[Pulse (2006 film)|Pulse]]'' (2006)\n| ''[[Pulse (2001 film)|Kairo]]'' (2001)\n|\n|-\n| ''[[The Ring (2002 film)|The Ring]]'' (2002)\n| ''[[Ring (film)|Ring]]'' (1998)\n| The novel ''[[Ring (Suzuki novel)|Ring]]'' ([[Koji Suzuki (writer)|Koji Suzuki]])\n|-\n| ''[[The Secret (2007 film)|The Secret]]'' (2007)\n| ''[[Himitsu (film)|Himitsu]]'' (1999)\n| The novel ''[[Naoko (novel)|Naoko]]'' ([[Keigo Higashino]])\n|-\n| ''[[Shall We Dance? (2004 film)|Shall We Dance?]]'' (2004)\n| ''[[Shall We Dance? (1996 film)|Shall We Dance?]]''